    <summary>Single-binary remote process/fs executor (hard-fork of codex exec-server)</summary>
    <description>
agentx is a single-binary remote process / filesystem executor — a hard fork
of `codex exec-server` from openai/codex rust-v0.142.0, owned by the
agentserver project. It registers a host with a control-plane URL via
WebSocket and streams process / fs RPCs.

See https://github.com/agentserver/agentx for usage.
